high_descs: Go forward, hang a right and go to the fridge, turn to the left, go to the dining table that is on the left.
Pick up the potato that is on the table.
Turn around, hang a right and go to the fridge that is on the left.
Put the potato inside the fridge and close the door, remove the potato from the fridge once it is cold.
Turn around, go forward, hang a left and cross the room to the microwave.
Put the potato inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk ahead a few steps, then turn right. Pass the table then turn left. Finally, turn left and face the table.
Pick up the potato on the right side of the table, near the loaf of bread.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Place the potato in the fridge, to the left of the white mug. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn around and walk to the left, all the way to the counter with the microwave on it.
Place the potato in the microwave, to the left of the mug.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled potato in a microwave.

take a few steps to the left, turn around to face fridge
